11\"><img alt=\"0206-DC3-E-B058-4-E2-D-A7-E9-ECF4941-FAA45\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/Wg969qf/0206-DC3-E-B058-4-E2-D-A7-E9-ECF4941-FAA45.png\"></a>  </p>\n<p>هذا الاختصار يدعم<br>\n<strong>Embed-a-Update</strong><br>\nوهو ضروري لإستلام إشعارات بأي تحديث للاختصار  </p>\n<p>This Shortcut supports <strong>Embed-a-Update</strong> which enables the Shortcut to check for updates and notify you about any available update.   </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://routinehub.co/shortcut/2672/\"><img alt=\"2-A207805-F5-BC-477-A-AF5-B-6-C24-CCF77-BA3\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/WFF9J9d/2-A207805-F5-BC-477-A-AF5-B-6-C24-CCF77-BA3.png\"></a></p>\n\t\t\t\t","releasenotes":"<p><strong>1.4 - Nov. 24, 2020, 10:34 a.m.</strong></p><p>Bug fixes.<br>No more third party update shortcuts (UpdateKit), Switching to [[Embed-a-Update]]. </p>"}